    },
    {
      "id": "pt_028c",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### PT-028c closed\n\nRomantic active progression needs psychological-comfort gradients and sentence-level intent instead of abrupt hard-push drafts\n\nNode: decision_recommendation",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 1470,
